        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Convert HEIC File to WebP Free Online:</strong> Use our online
          tool to freely convert HEIC to WebP.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="my-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">
        Why Convert HEIC to WEBP
